275
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,240
Okay.

276
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:42,740
Co to je?

277
00:29:42,740 --> 00:29:45,210
Co to balíte?

278
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:49,880
Organizuju svoje knížky.

279
00:29:54,630 --> 00:29:58,280
